{"tid":901620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"運房局：高鐵約70%乘客非本地居民","createTime":"2018-11-14T07:20:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T08:44:05.000Z","uid":144372,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5dc54cef7acedf9bb9b31972168e16053e04a915","tid":901620,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T07:20:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%AB%98%E9%90%B5%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%AE%B5%E6%AF%8F%E6%97%A5%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E5%AE%A2%E9%87%8F%E7%B4%84%E4%BA%94%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%A1-%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E4%BD%94%E4%B8%89%E6%88%90-064852936.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%2590%25B5%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25AE%25B5%25E6%25AF%258F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%259D%2587%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E9%2587%258F%25E7%25B4%2584%25E4%25BA%2594%25E8%2590%25AC%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%25A1-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25BD%2594%25E4%25B8%2589%25E6%2588%2590-064852936.html&d=wYIrc0MOATNyAI01%2F0rN1G6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=b3fd7f44\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%AB%98%E9%90%B5%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%AE%B5%E6%AF%8F%E6%97%A5%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E5%AE%A2%E9%87%8F%E7%B4%84%E4%BA%94%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%A1-%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E4%BD%94%E4%B8%89%E6%88%90-064852936.html</a><br />\n<br />\n運輸及房屋局書面回覆立法會質詢時表示，廣深港高鐵香港段投入服務以來，截至10月31日，總乘客量為198萬5937人次，平均每日乘客量為50921人次，香港乘客佔總乘客量約3成，內地及外國國籍的乘客佔總乘客量約7成。<br />\n<br />\n運房局又表示，由於港鐵以商業模式營運，《服務經營權補充協議》中的財務估算方法及數字均屬商業敏感資料，不宜公開。高鐵香港段開通至今，乘客量從未觸及《服務經營權補充協議》的「乘客量上下限機制」預期乘客量的下限，即九鐵公司不需要賠償予港鐵，又說按機制計算，個別日子乘客量波幅不會影響是否需要啟動相關機制。<br />\n<br />\n運房局表示，當局重點是高鐵香港段在10年經營期能夠做到財務健康穩健，不需九鐵公司補貼，港鐵公司作為上市公司亦可取得合理的商業回報。"},{"pid":"4cddb86a57309998dd28d22cad76076605142c0b","tid":901620,"uid":53026,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T08:44:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180924/large/24la4p4new.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180924%2Flarge%2F24la4p4new.jpg&h=14a8ccc8&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}